Crypt-AllOrNothing

VERSION

	0.10

CURRENT STATUS

	All functions working, in Beta release.  Please let me know about any bugs.
	Currently only 128 bits is supported for size of packets

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Crypt::AllOrNothing

You can also look for information at:

	Read the paper
		http://people.csail.mit.edu/rivest/Fusion.ps

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Crypt-AllOrNothing

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Crypt-AllOrNothing

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Crypt-AllOrNothing

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Crypt-AllOrNothing

